---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to My World! 👋</h1>
			<p>
				Hi there! I'm IR, and I'm thrilled you're here. This is my personal space where I share my thoughts, stories, and passion for life - from family and fitness to soccer and gaming.
			</p>
			<p>
				Whether you're here by chance or intention, I hope you find something that resonates with you. Feel free to explore, read my blog posts, and get to know me better. Let's connect!
			</p>
			<p><strong>Here's what you can do on this site:</strong></p>
			<ul>
				<li>Read my blog posts and share in my journey</li>
				<li>Learn more about me on the <a href="/about">About page</a></li>
				<li>Discover my thoughts on life, family, and passions</li>
				<li>Stay updated with my latest stories and reflections</li>
				<li>Connect with the real me through my words</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				I'm always excited to hear from visitors. If you have any thoughts, questions, or just want to say hello - don't hesitate to reach out. Thank you for stopping by, and I hope you enjoy your visit!
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
